task: FIX v2-string-split-limit-overload (BUGS.md) — String.split(delimiter, limit), the two-arg overload, is unimplemented on the v2 VM ("no dispatch for .split"); one-arg split(delimiter) works. Caused a real busi production outage. Repro at tests/conformance/v2-string-split-limit-overload.ssc.
